event.title: Highest temperature in Chicago on Oct 30, 2024?

markets.subtitle: 76° or below
markets.rules_primary: If the highest temperature recorded at Chicago Midway, IL for October 30, 2024, is less than 77° according to the NWS's Daily Climate Report, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary:
Please be advised to check to see what temperatures have occurred previously in the day. While the market resolves based on the finalized report from the NWS, traders should use other data sources--including other preliminary NWS reporting--to inform their trades.

The Last Trading Time will be 11:59 PM ET on October 30, 2024 regardless of any data releases or events occurring. Expiration will occur on the sooner of the first 7:00 or 8:00
AM ET following the release of the data for October 30, 2024, or one week after October 30, 2024.

As a reminder, the Underlying is not the NWS NOWData data source. As noted in the Rulebook, for the actual Underlying, please go to the Source Agency link, click on "Observed Weather", then choose "Chicago Midway, IL".
